


- Download Deploy Script for Agent (https://server_url/api/v1/deploy/?api_key=<api_key>)
- Running Script
- Install Dependency 1st(apt-get update && apt-get install git curl)
- Git cloning for Agents Source (https://github.com/ardikabs/fipro-agent.git) dan ditempatkan pada /var/fipro-agents

- Install Dependency 2nd(docker && docker-compose && etc) from installer in /var/fipro-agents/script/install.sh

- Set CWD (Current Working Directory) pada /var/fipro-agents/docker

- Running Multiple Services
	- FluentBit-service ( with configuration in /var/fipro-agents/docker/fluentbit/conf)
	- Agent-service

